        public void reduce(K key,
          ReducerInput<V> values)
        Description copied from class: Reducer
        Processes the values for a given key, using the context returned by Worker.getContext() to emit output to the Output of the MapReduce. values enumerates all values that the map phase produced for the key key. It will always contain at least one value.
